{"tid":378414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長和旗下和電遭印度追稅，長和：對方不可能有效收稅","createTime":"2017-08-28T13:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T14:43:44.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04b9bbcaea309714256883a1fad4b17a119b6fb5","tid":378414,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/sing1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fsing1.png&h=b6c0ddd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長江和記實業有限公司（00001）宣布，旗下和電國際早在2007年向Vodafone出售印度電訊業務，惟本年初遭印度政府追收約 790 億印度盧比（約96 億港元）的資本收益稅，再加上利息約1643億印度盧比（約200億港元）。長和認為印度政府不可能對和電徵稅。<br />\n<br />\n長和在聲明中表示，和電國際多年前向Vodafone出售的印度電訊業務是為CGP Investments  Limited，除了在本年2月接獲印度稅務局發之評稅令下，更在8月9日再收到對方發出的罰款令，罰款金額約 790 億印度盧比（約 96 億港元）；包括利息及之前的資本收益稅合共約400億港元。<br />\n<br />\n不過長和認為，印度當局不可能對和電國際徵收以上稅項、利息和罰款；和電取得之法律意見指，印度政府仍然會按追補法例發出上述法令，籍此推翻印度最高法院於2012年1月作出的裁決，即裁定收購事項無須在印度課稅，故屬違反國際法律之原則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170618/large/1497768656_ecab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170618%2Flarge%2F1497768656_ecab.jpg&h=1c7e7496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/08/28/article/33950/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2Farticle%2F33950%2F&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=98e7cbdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/08/28/article/33950/</a>"},{"pid":"04e1d17896ece7666aa6ab5f64f4e92dfa0818b6","tid":378414,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"搞支那搞到誠哥頭上"},{"pid":"9cb9f3505dc4c6f876e1ff1fc7c9ea1ae8e5eef2","tid":378414,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搞支那搞到誠哥頭上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n誠哥係加拿大人"},{"pid":"c5b6e304951bf821f0a6d23b95f84842fd5b9674","tid":378414,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d6408b07d5dce5f0c1bca3634517ad834c6e875","tid":378414,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31eec2dd9557e97303094ff35517954afa89bd1","tid":378414,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗"},{"pid":"88af84877d5b85c1b5526fc0b3a66f5e410dec1f","tid":378414,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"我係佢我就交咗佢<br />\n200億港紙都買到啲飛機大砲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3b524efb3336cacbafb28e1506593e51a23aa1","tid":378414,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"印度真係冇乜輸出賺錢<br />\n唯一諗到係IT人<br />\n一係ban鳩哂阿差入境"},{"pid":"c7894f1c654d82be8f4b84be2669753597a998b6","tid":378414,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"最高法院判左仲追咩？？"}]}